request URL: protocol://location/path/file.ext

input/output (TODO: Use libcurl if available)
----------------------------------------------
  * io
    - protocol
      + direct
        - file open/close
        - file descriptor read/write
        * extension (file name extension)
      + http
        - socket open/close
        - file descriptor read/write
        * extension (content-type)


file extension (container format)
----------------------------------------------
  * extension
    + wav (pcm, mp3)
      - handle container header
      * format
    + ogg (pcm, speex, vorbis, opus, flac)
      - handle container header
      * format
    + raw (pcm, mp3, flac)
      * format


data format
----------------------------------------------
  * format
    + pcm
      - big/little endian
      - floats
      - compressed
      - integer
        - signed/unsigned 
    + mp3
    + vorbis
    + speex
    = opus
    + flac


